article_title: Are People Getting More Care Or Better Care Under Obamacare? No

article_metadata.author: John C. Goodman

og.description: By one estimate, 14 million people are newly insured because of the Affordable Care Act. In addition millions of others have more generous insurance, promising new benefits. So you might expect that doctors’ offices would be flooded with a host of new patients seeking more care than they had before. It’s [...]
